                     <title xml:lang="en">A submission from Siwa (evidently the Mahratta Shiwaji) to Aurangzib.</title>
                     <note>Shiwaji (and his Persian secretaries?). For further details see Codrington/Reade No 345 (1). Work is a firmly stated protest against Aurangzib's imposition of the jizya on the Hindus. Scribe is probably Muhammad Muhammadi (?), scribe of Codrington/Reade 345 (3)</note>
                     <incipit>'Ardah-dasht-i khair-khwah-i rasikh-dam</incipit>
